{
  "page": "Lord Corbray (father of Lyonel)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\"><img alt=\"House Corbray.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/50px-House_Corbray.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/75px-House_Corbray.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/100px-House_Corbray.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Corbray</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\"><img alt=\"House Corbray.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/50px-House_Corbray.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/75px-House_Corbray.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/100px-House_Corbray.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nOld Lord Corbray<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Lord of Heart&#39;s Home\">Lord of Heart's Home</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">House Corbray</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Corbray\" title=\"Lyonel Corbray\">Lyonel Corbray</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn Corbray</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lucas_Corbray\" title=\"Lucas Corbray\">Lucas Corbray</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Lord Corbray</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">House Corbray</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Corbray_(father_of_Lyonel)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>He was an old man by the time of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>. He wielded the ancestral <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Longsword\" title=\"Longsword\">longsword</a> of his house, <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Forlorn\" title=\"Lady Forlorn\">Lady Forlorn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Corbray_(father_of_Lyonel)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord Corbray fought for Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a>. He was wounded during the battle and his eldest son and heir, <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Corbray\" title=\"Lyonel Corbray\">Lyonel</a>, carried him back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">maesters</a> in the rear, while his second son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn</a>, grabbed his sword, <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Forlorn\" title=\"Lady Forlorn\">Lady Forlorn</a>, and led a charge against the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a> led by Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Lewyn_Martell\" title=\"Lewyn Martell\">Lewyn Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Corbray was eventually succeeded by Lyonel, but gave Lady Forlorn to Lyn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Corbray_(father_of_Lyonel)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rows